{"tid":1988624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【軍心post】重啟每日鳩叫兼DSE打氣（再post)","createTime":"2020-04-25T10:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T00:43:20.000Z","uid":229642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad25bb2d28a159ca7c5b2944c967374a99ba939","tid":1988624,"uid":229642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重振軍心！咪再受影響</span><br />\n呢輪日日講鬥黃點點點，不如講點團結啲，有返士氣啲？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁多人日日留係屋企，鳩叫最好良機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間考慮：為免影響一啲長期病患者同考生正常休息時間，改中午、傍晚（實際時間同星期幾定日日鳩叫大家可以再傾）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">內容：除咗光復香港時代革命五大訴求缺一不可，可以宣傳多啲文宣口號同dse打氣，甚至一人講一句文宣接落去，例如：你若肺炎誰棄我城之類大家熟啦，時間維持十五分鐘至半個鍾</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應對藍絲鄰居：佢哋罵可以用啲講林鄭唔封關搞到大家咁、中共搞到全球嘅文宣、是旦塞鳩佢地轉頭</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有咩大家一齊傾掂，咪鬼再畀對家挫士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"871645835e1b29fb701bd720d1fd70e3deb81669","tid":1988624,"uid":229642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"有人話我開錯台所以先無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cbe8187c859886bfeea346a88b09bf9cca21c9","tid":1988624,"uid":229642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"軍心呀！dse考生好需要大家